Attributes.description: Introduction to the origin and diversity of protists (protozoa and algae) at both cellular and genomic levels, including the role of endosymbiosis in evolution.
Attributes.prereq: Pre-reqs: (Either (a) BIOL 121 and one of BIOL 180, BIOL 140; or (b) SCIE 001 or (c) BIOL121 and 2nd-year standing in Combined Honours Biophysics, or (d) 8 transfer credits of first-year biology.)
